#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""lore — one lens over the memory AI coding agents accumulate.

Single-file, standard-library-only. v0a: source enumeration + adapter framework
+ the Claude adapter + read-only commands (ls/search/show/graph/stats/export).
v0b: the token-overlap scorer + opt-in LLM commands (summarize/relevant) via the
Anthropic Messages API over stdlib HTTP (no SDK; auth from ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in the
env or $SANDY_HOME/.secrets). The read-only core stays fully functional with no key
and no network. No mutation, no non-Claude adapters (later increments).
"""
